                        "displayName": "Joris Van den Bossche",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Brussels"
                    },
                    "body": "For the options or checked vs non checked, we indeed need to pick some default, but I think that's OK (and I would indeed also go for the checked versions).\r\n\r\nI think _if_ we add those, we should also change the behaviour of {{__eq__}}, although that is something that will require a long deprecation cycle.",
